(\Omega, \mathcal F)
f:\Omega\rightarrow\mathbb R
\mathbb P_1,\dots,\mathbb P_N
i=1,\dots,N
(a_{k,i})_{k\in\mathbb N}\subset\mathbb R
(A_{k,i})_{k\in\mathbb N}\subset\mathcal F
(b_k)_{k\in\mathbb N}\subset\mathbb R
B_k\in\mathcal F
i=1,\dots,N
f=\sum_{k=1}^\infty a_{k,i}\cdot 1_{A_{k,i}}\ \ \mathbb P_i-a.s.
f=\sum_{k=1}^\infty b_{k}\cdot 1_{B_{k}} \mathbb\ \ \mathbb P_i-a.s.
